body_html: You can do pip uninstall tensorflow-tensorboard and then pip install tensorflow-tensorboard==<your_version>. At least this is what I do as long as pip installs the wrong tensorflow-tensorboard version.

body: You can do `pip uninstall tensorflow-tensorboard` and then `pip install tensorflow-tensorboard==<your_version>`. At least this is what I do as long as pip installs the wrong tensorflow-tensorboard version.
